      <aside class="rv-panel">
        <h2>on the floor</h2>
        <ol id="rvBoard"><li><span>the floor awaits…</span></li></ol>
        <h2 class="rv-panel__h2">your night</h2>
        <div class="rv-stats" id="rvStats"></div>
        <button class="rv-share-btn" id="rvShareNight">📸 share my night</button>
        <div class="rv-door">
          <a href="/make-a-banana/" data-place="rave">Dress your banana &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        <p class="rv-note"><strong>Boogie with the arrow keys / WASD, or tap the floor.</strong> Everything else — Barty, the jelly, the drops — is in <a href="#what">the field guide below ↓</a></p>
      </aside>
    </div>

    <!-- ============ below the floor: what this place IS ============ -->
    <div class="rvg">
      <section class="rvg__block" id="what">
        <p class="rvg__kicker">the fine print, in neon</p>
        <h2>what is this place?</h2>
        <p>
          In 1999 I drew <a href="/dancing-banana-gif-meme/">a little banana that never stopped dancing</a>.
          Twenty-seven years later, it has a club. <strong>Every banana on this floor is a real visitor</strong> —
          no bots, no fakes. The only characters who aren't guests are staff: Barty behind the bar and
          tonight's DJ in the booth. They have jobs.
        </p>
        <p>
          And here's the trick the whole place runs on: <strong>there is only one song, and it never
          stops.</strong> Every banana on Earth dances on the same beat — open the rave on your phone and
          your laptop and watch them match, frame for frame. Same beat, whole planet.
        </p>
        <p>No account. No cost. Your banana walks in <a href="/make-a-banana/">dressed the way you left it in the builder</a>, or a fresh one is generated at the door.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="rvg__block" id="do">
        <p class="rvg__kicker">the loop</p>
        <h2>what do you actually do here?</h2>
        <ul class="rvg__list">
          <li><strong>Boogie.</strong> Arrow keys, WASD, or tap the floor. The dance never stops — walking is just dancing with direction.</li>
          <li><strong>Chase what the floor spawns.</strong> Jelly drops, snacks, power-ups, the lost vinyl, the golden banana — being first is the sport. Everything you grab fills the <strong>JELLY meter</strong>; a full meter is yours to spend on a personal drop.</li>
          <li><strong>Help Barty.</strong> He knows you're here to rave — but could you help an old banana with a few chores? Finish his requests and he stamps your <strong>nightshift</strong>. Five shifts make you a regular, with a regular's privileges.</li>
          <li><strong>Outlast everyone.</strong> Survive 5 minutes and the stage opens: dance behind the DJ, earn the &#128293; emote. Survive 30 and the glowstick is yours forever. The endurance board remembers.</li>
          <li><strong>Make a name.</strong> Everything you do pays into your club LEVEL — the gold bar by the JELLY meter, 1 to 99, forever. Climb the brackets and the roster shows your title in gold: On the List, The Regular, VIP… Legend of the Floor.</li>
          <li><strong>Collect the marks.</strong> Everything you earn here lands on <a href="/pass/">your banana pass</a> — badges, gear, level, stats. The rave writes your history.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="rvg__block" id="guide">
        <p class="rvg__kicker">field guide</p>
        <h2>who &amp; what is on the floor</h2>
        <p class="rvg__sub">Everything below is the actual pixel art from the club, at actual chunkiness.</p>
        <div class="rvg__grid">
          {GUIDE.map((g) => (
            <article class="rvg__card">
              <div class="rvg__thumb"><img src={G + g.img + '.png'} alt={g.name + ' — banana rave pixel sprite'} loading="lazy" /></div>
              <h3>{g.name}</h3>
              <p>{g.text}</p>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="rvg__block" id="clock">
        <p class="rvg__kicker">the rhythm</p>
        <h2>the club runs on a clock</h2>
        <p>Nothing here is random — the whole planet shares one schedule. Stay long enough and you'll feel it:</p>
        <ul class="rvg__list rvg__list--clock">
          <li><strong>every ~75 seconds</strong> — the conveyor drops something chaseable</li>
          <li><strong>every 2 minutes</strong> — the spotlight wanders; dancing inside it is bonus jelly</li>
          <li><strong>every 3rd minute</strong> — THE DROP. Strobes, pyro, everybody peaks</li>
          <li><strong>every 5th minute</strong> — HAPPY HOUR at the bar (and specials in between)</li>
          <li><strong>every 7 minutes</strong> — the DJ loses a vinyl. Again.</li>
          <li><strong>every 8 minutes</strong> — THE WAVE. Barty yells, the floor ripples</li>
          <li><strong>every 30 minutes</strong> — the golden banana. Once. Somewhere.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="rvg__block" id="faq">
        <p class="rvg__kicker">the usual questions</p>
        <h2>banana rave FAQ</h2>
        <div class="rvg__faq">
          <h3>Is it really live?</h3>
          <p>Yes. Every banana is a real visitor, right now. When the floor is quiet, that's honesty, not failure — bring a friend.</p>
          <h3>Why is everyone in perfect sync?</h3>
          <p>One song, one wall clock, every banana on Earth on the same beat. It's the oldest trick in the club and it never misses.</p>
          <h3>Why does the club never close?</h3>
          <p>Somebody's always on shift. Finish your chores and Barty stamps you out — <em>"nightshift's done, back to clubbing"</em> — but the music was playing before you arrived and it'll play after you leave.</p>
          <h3>What's the JELLY meter?</h3>
          <p>The gauge of the night. Jelly drops, snacks, chores, the spotlight, surviving drops — it all fills it. Full meter = it starts flashing, and tapping it drops the floor — just for you.</p>
          <h3>What's my LEVEL?</h3>
          <p>Your standing at the club, 1 to 99 — the gold bar under the JELLY meter. Every jelly, pickup and chore pays into it, it syncs across your devices with <a href="/pass/">your pass</a>, and it never goes down. Titles land at the big levels, and the floor roster shows them in gold — the room knows who's a regular.</p>
          <h3>Do my things carry over?</h3>
          <p>Everything. Badges and stats live on <a href="/pass/">your pass</a>, earned gear like the glowstick follows your banana into <a href="/make-a-banana/">the builder</a>, and the stool waits for its regular.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="rvg__block rvg__block--doors" id="doors">
        <p class="rvg__kicker">more banana</p>
        <h2>before you go (or instead of going)</h2>
        <div class="rvg__doors">
          <a href="/make-a-banana/" data-place="rave-guide">Dress your banana →</a>
          <a href="/pass/">Check your pass →</a>
          <a href="/dancing-banana-gif-meme/">Download the original GIF →</a>
          <a href="/dancing-banana-remixes/">The community remixes →</a>
          <a href="/wall/">The banana wall →</a>
          <a href="/shop/">The banana shop →</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

